data.description: *** BRAND NEW ARCHITECTURAL ROOF COMING SOON--- MARCH 2021 *** QUIET NW ALBANY CUL DE SAC - GREAT LOCATION - LOADS OF SPACE FOR THE PRICE!!!  Beautiful split level brick home features nearly 3,000 sq ft of living space, 3 bedrooms, 3 baths plus a large bonus room, office space (could be a 4th bedroom or private downstairs suite) and so much more!  The main level features most of your everyday living space including a large formal living/dining area, kitchen with pretty wooden cabinets, a breakfast bar space and is open to the den, a secondary den space, 3 spacious bedrooms and 3 full baths!  Very pretty hardwood floors!   Downstairs would make a great private suite--includes a large bonus room, separate office space and a full bath!  Additional features/upgrades include storm windows, an updated roof, new HVAC unit (2018), a double carport, a nice open deck area (great entertaining space), a fenced pet/garden space and a detached storage building/workshop space!  A LARGE FAMILY HOME FOR A SUPER LOW PRICE!
